            "title": "大公司创新情报（5月8日）：顾家家居：拟向特定对象盈峰集团发行股票 募集资金总额不超19.97亿元",
            "description": "<article class=\"post-body\" data-v-1d7d601f=\"\">\n<h3 style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">今日看点</span>\n</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/65c240a7b7018f6c2fac332919aa91f4?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\">顾家家居：拟向特定对象盈峰集团发行股票 募集资金总额不超19.97亿元</strong></a><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;display: block;\">\n</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/7f4550354717d108f8ca967fd5fcfb65?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\">天合光能中标国家电投2025年储能系统集采600MWh订单</strong></a><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;display: block;\">\n</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/b4215d636854c8fca3197edae9e2edcf?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\">开源证券：物管行业转型有望改善盈利能力 “资产荒”下REITs性价比持续提升</strong></a><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;display: block;\">\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:11pt\">\n<br/>\n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n        今日情报（17家18条）\n    </h3>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/d9db48a36b1bff2e6b4eb563155b351a/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">顾家家居</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/65c240a7b7018f6c2fac332919aa91f4?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">顾家家居：拟向特定对象盈峰集团发行股票 募集资金总额不超19.97亿元</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/37b1afcea010c37e1683f44e53e9da62/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">天合光能</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/7f4550354717d108f8ca967fd5fcfb65?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">天合光能中标国家电投2025年储能系统集采600MWh订单</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/bb6f0c534640f3cee8be556372caf088/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">华润万象生活</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/b4215d636854c8fca3197edae9e2edcf?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">开源证券：物管行业转型有望改善盈利能力 “资产荒”下REITs性价比持续提升</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/dd88e183fc79ab787be7e1cd4cb3da47/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">宁德时代</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/bf7622ad617a54eb146d2557c7d98df8?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">万亿市值“宁王”，赴港IPO通过聆讯</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/3abac56002850c725f953ec5009b7172/profile?s